#. (itstool) path: listitem/para
#. (itstool) id: book.translate.xml#zfs-advanced-tuning-arc_max
#: book.translate.xml:40355
msgid "<emphasis><varname>vfs.zfs.arc_max</varname></emphasis> - Maximum size of the <link linkend=\"zfs-term-arc\"><acronym>ARC</acronym></link>. The default is all <acronym>RAM</acronym> less 1 GB, or one half of <acronym>RAM</acronym>, whichever is more. However, a lower value should be used if the system will be running any other daemons or processes that may require memory. This value can only be adjusted at boot time, and is set in <filename>/boot/loader.conf</filename>."
